# Security Policy

## Reporting a vulnerability

If you believe you have found a security vulnerability in {{PROJECT_NAME}}, please report it
privately so it can be fixed before it is disclosed publicly.

- **Contact:** {{CONTACT}}
- Include a description of the issue, the steps to reproduce it, and the impact you expect.
- Please do **not** open a public issue for security problems.

You can expect an acknowledgement within a few days. Once the issue is confirmed we will work on
a fix and coordinate a disclosure timeline with you.

## Supported versions

Security fixes land on the latest released version. Older versions are supported on a best-effort
basis only.
